DID YOU JUST GET HERE?

68
00:04:20,250 --> 00:04:21,666
- YEAH.
JUST A MOMENT AGO.

69
00:04:21,750 --> 00:04:23,833
- YOU'RE LOOKING GOOD.
I'M GLAD TO SEE YOU BACK HERE.

70
00:04:23,916 --> 00:04:25,250
- THANK YOU SO MUCH.

71
00:04:25,333 --> 00:04:27,000
- I'M GLAD YOU'RE BACK
AT HEADQUARTERS.

72
00:04:27,083 --> 00:04:28,833
I REALLY TRULY AM.

73
00:04:28,916 --> 00:04:31,375
SINCE YOU WERE DEMOTED
TO SUCH A REMOTE AREA,

74
00:04:31,458 --> 00:04:33,916
WELL, WE ALL THOUGHT THAT
WAS THE END OF YOUR CAREER.

75
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:36,458
- OH, REALLY?

76
00:04:36,541 --> 00:04:39,458
- SAY, KIYONE,
