MINOR INCIDENTAL UNIT JOBS, HUH?

91
00:05:12,166 --> 00:05:14,083
GOOD FOR YOU, KID.

92
00:05:14,166 --> 00:05:16,375
YOU'LL HAVE A LOT OF TIME
TO KICK BACK AND RELAX.

93
00:05:16,458 --> 00:05:17,666
I'D BETTER BE GOING.

94
00:05:19,166 --> 00:05:22,958
KIYONE?
I'LL SEE YOU AROUND.

95
00:05:23,041 --> 00:05:25,958
- ( mumbles, shouts )

96
00:05:26,041 --> 00:05:29,083
WHY THAT NASTY AWFUL LOUSY--

97
00:05:33,041 --> 00:05:35,875
