98
00:05:37,916 --> 00:05:40,541
DETECTIVE FIRST CLASS KIYONE
REPORTING FOR DUTY

99
00:05:40,625 --> 00:05:43,583
TO THE CRIMINAL INVESTIGATION
UNIT NINE AT HEADQUARTERS

100
00:05:43,666 --> 00:05:45,208
AS OF TODAY.

101
00:05:45,291 --> 00:05:47,916
- WE'VE BEEN WAITING FOR
YOUR ARRIVAL, DETECTIVE.

102
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:49,291
- HM?

103
00:05:51,750 --> 00:05:52,916
- I'VE HEARD A LOT ABOUT YOU

104
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:55,250
SINCE YOU WERE IN
THE POLICE ACADEMY.

105
00:05:55,333 --> 00:05:58,583
I ALWAYS THOUGHT YOU WERE TOO
GOOD TO BE A RESIDENT OFFICER

106
00:05:58,666 --> 00:06:00,000
IN A REMOTE REGION.

107
00:06:00,083 --> 00:06:01,250
- THANKS VERY MUCH, SIR.

108
00:06:01,333 --> 00:06:02,666
- NOW THAT YOU ARE HERE,

109
00:06:02,750 --> 00:06:05,000
I EXPECT TO SEE YOU PERFORM
UP TO YOUR ABILITY.

110
00:06:05,083 --> 00:06:07,583
- YES, SIR.

111
00:06:07,666 --> 00:06:09,458
- KIYONE,

112
00:06:09,541 --> 00:06:11,541
IT HAS COME TO MY ATTENTION

113
00:06:11,625 --> 00:06:13,000
THAT YOU WERE WITH
PRINCESS AYEKA

114
00:06:13,083 --> 00:06:15,208
OF THE PLANET JURAI
WHILE YOU WERE ON EARTH?

115
00:06:15,291 --> 00:06:18,208
- YES. BY A STRANGE
TURN OF EVENTS.

116
00:06:18,291 --> 00:06:19,750
I THOUGHT I'D ALREADY
EXPLAINED ALL THAT

117
00:06:19,833 --> 00:06:20,875
IN MY REPORT, SIR.

118
00:06:20,958 --> 00:06:22,583
- YES, YOU DID.

119
00:06:22,666 --> 00:06:25,583
DETECTIVE, RIGHT NOW
THE GALAXY POLICE

120
00:06:25,666 --> 00:06:27,375
