00:06:53,041 --> 00:06:55,125
- WE INTERRUPT OUR
REGULAR PROGRAMS

128
00:06:55,208 --> 00:06:56,625
FOR AN EMERGENCY BROADCAST

129
00:06:56,708 --> 00:06:59,458
REGARDING BREAKING NEWS
FROM THE PLANET JURAI. 

130
00:06:59,541 --> 00:07:01,291
AS WE HAVE ALREADY
INFORMED YOU,

131
00:07:01,375 --> 00:07:04,250
