136
00:07:12,166 --> 00:07:14,166
- SHUT UP, AYEKA.
WE CAN'T HEAR THE NEWS.

137
00:07:14,250 --> 00:07:16,833
- AYEKA, PLEASE BE QUIET.

138
00:07:16,916 --> 00:07:18,291
- THE THRONE HAS BEEN
TEMPORARILY VACANT

139
00:07:18,375 --> 00:07:20,625
PENDING MARRIAGE BY
THE PRINCESS AYEKA.

140
00:07:20,708 --> 00:07:23,291
