SINCE THE SUDDEN ASCENDANCE
OF THE NEW EMPEROR YOSHO

142
00:07:26,958 --> 00:07:27,916
TO THE THRONE.

143
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:29,166
- ( gasps )
