144
00:07:29,250 --> 00:07:31,833
 ANNOUNCES THAT EVERYTHING
IS UNDER CONTROL.

145
00:07:31,916 --> 00:07:33,666
- YOSHO?

146
00:07:33,750 --> 00:07:37,625
HOW COULD IT BE? 
IT IS IMPOSSIBLE.

147
00:07:37,708 --> 00:07:39,083
- YOSHO?

148
00:07:39,166 --> 00:07:42,083
- YES, THAT'S THE NAME OF
JURAI'S NEW EMPEROR.

149
00:07:42,166 --> 00:07:43,333
- DETECTIVE SERGEANT,

150
00:07:43,416 --> 00:07:45,083
I DON'T REMEMBER HAVING
SEEN THAT NAME

151
00:07:45,166 --> 00:07:47,000
AMONG THE SUCCESSORS
TO THE THRONE.

152
00:07:48,166 --> 00:07:49,333
- HMM.

153
00:07:49,416 --> 00:07:50,333
KIYONE!

154
00:07:50,416 --> 00:07:51,958
- THAT'S QUITE ALL RIGHT.

155
00:07:53,875 --> 00:07:56,125
YOU MAY NOT HAVE
HEARD OF HIM,

156
00:07:56,208 --> 00:07:58,583
BUT YOSHO IS THE
LEGITIMATE SUCCESSOR

157
00:07:58,666 --> 00:08:00,125
TO JURAI'S ROYAL FAMILY,

158
00:08:00,208 --> 00:08:02,583
AND A LEGENDARY WARRIOR.

159
00:08:02,666 --> 00:08:06,208
HE CAME BACK
TO THE PLANET JURAI.

160
00:08:06,291 --> 00:08:09,708
- I JUST CANNOT
BELIEVE ANY OF THIS.

161
00:08:09,791 --> 00:08:11,916
- AYEKA.

162
00:08:12,000 --> 00:08:15,541
- OH, THE LEGENDARY WARRIOR
YOSHO.

163
00:08:15,625 --> 00:08:17,541
I HAVE HEARD THAT NAME
SO VERY MANY TIMES

164
00:08:17,625 --> 00:08:19,666
SINCE MY CHILDHOOD
ON PLANET JURAI.

165
00:08:19,750 --> 00:08:22,208
- THE LEGENDARY WARRIOR?

166
00:08:22,291 --> 00:08:23,666
WHO IS HE ANYWAY?

167
00:08:23,750 --> 00:08:26,875
- HE IS SAID TO BE THE BEST
SWORDSMAN IN THE EMPIRE.

168
00:08:26,958 --> 00:08:28,708
AND HE IS A NOBLE PRINCE

169
00:08:28,791 --> 00:08:31,291
GIFTED WITH BOTH
INTELLIGENCE AND COURAGE.

170
00:08:31,375 --> 00:08:34,583
BUT HE GAVE UP HIS POSITION
AS THE SUCCESSOR

171
00:08:34,666 --> 00:08:36,291
AND JUST DISAPPEARED.

172
00:08:36,375 --> 00:08:38,958
THAT WAS MANY DECADES AGO.

173
00:08:44,666 --> 00:08:46,291
WHY...

174
00:08:46,375 --> 00:08:48,500
WHY WOULD HE SUDDENLY
COME FORWARD?

175
00:08:48,583 --> 00:08:50,625
- I'LL TELL YOU.
HE'S PROBABLY A FAKE.

176
00:08:50,708 --> 00:08:53,291
IT'S AN OLD TRICK
USED BY A CONMAN.

177
00:08:53,375 --> 00:08:55,291
- CAN'T BE.

178
00:08:55,375 --> 00:08:57,583
AT LEAST HE IS
A ROYAL FAMILY MEMBER.

179
00:08:57,666 --> 00:08:59,583
OF THAT,
WE CAN ALL BE SURE.

180
00:08:59,666 --> 00:09:01,166
- WHY DO YOU SAY THAT?

181
00:09:03,500 --> 00:09:05,166
- BECAUSE OF JURAI'S POWER.

182
00:09:05,250 --> 00:09:06,625
- THE POWER.

183
00:09:06,708 --> 00:09:07,958
IT'S BECAUSE OF THE POWER

184
00:09:08,041 --> 00:09:10,625
ONLY JURAI'S ROYAL
FAMILY MEMBERS POSSESS.

185
00:09:10,708 --> 00:09:12,791
JURAI'S POWER IS SAID

186
00:09:12,875 --> 00:09:15,291
TO EVEN SURPASS
THE POWER OF GOD.

187
00:09:15,375 --> 00:09:18,333
WITHOUT A DEMONSTRATION
OF THIS AWESOME POWER, 

188
00:09:18,416 --> 00:09:22,000
THE COUNCIL WOULDN'T HAVE 
APPROVED THE ENTHRONEMENT.

189
00:09:25,291 --> 00:09:28,625
BESIDES, I SAW IT
WITH MY OWN EYES.

190
00:09:30,166 --> 00:09:33,083
I WITNESSED HOW POWERFUL
YOSHO IS.

191
00:09:35,166 --> 00:09:37,791
- DISSATISFIED WITH
THE ENTHRONEMENT OF YOSHO,

192
00:09:37,875 --> 00:09:39,666
PRINCESS AYEKA
ATTEMPTED A COUP

193
00:09:39,750 --> 00:09:42,291
AND IS NOW CONSIDERED 
A FUGITIVE ON THE RUN.

194
00:09:42,375 --> 00:09:43,333
- ( spits )

195
00:09:43,416 --> 00:09:46,208
- COUP DE TAT?  ME?!
ARE THEY CRAZY?

196
00:09:46,291 --> 00:09:48,750
- YOU ARE SO BAD,
AYEKA, YOU KNOW? 

197
00:09:48,833 --> 00:09:50,083
YOU DIDN'T HAVE TO DO THAT

198
00:09:50,166 --> 00:09:52,125
JUST BECAUSE YOU DIDN'T
MAKE IT TO THE THRONE. 

199
00:09:52,208 --> 00:09:53,666
- OH, RYOKO!

200
00:09:53,750 --> 00:09:56,125
- ( chuckles )
HEY, COME ON, AYEKA.

201
00:09:56,208 --> 00:09:57,500
THAT'S WHAT IT SAID ON TV.

202
00:09:57,583 --> 00:09:58,791
WHAT?!

203
00:09:58,875 --> 00:10:00,375
- THIS IS A PICTURE OF THE
SPACE PIRATE RYOKO,

204
00:10:00,458 --> 00:10:02,500
WHO IS ACTING TOGETHER
WITH PRINCESS AYEKA.

205
00:10:02,583 --> 00:10:04,375
RYOKO HAS BEEN
A MOST WANTED CRIMINAL

206
00:10:04,458 --> 00:10:05,791
FOR QUITE SOME TIME NOW.

207
00:10:05,875 --> 00:10:07,458
AND IT IS BELIEVED
SHE PLAYED A MAJOR PART

208
00:10:07,541 --> 00:10:09,458
IN THE ATTEMPTED COUP.

209
00:10:09,541 --> 00:10:10,791
- ( groans )

210
00:10:10,875 --> 00:10:13,041
WHY WOULD I WANT TO HELP
AYEKA WITH HER CONSPIRACY,

211
00:10:13,125 --> 00:10:14,500
STUPID NEWS GUY?

212
00:10:14,583 --> 00:10:16,333
- LOOK. JUST BY STANDING
NEXT TO YOU,

213
00:10:16,416 --> 00:10:18,833
EVEN I LOOK LIKE
A CRIMINAL.

214
00:10:18,916 --> 00:10:20,125
- LISTEN, YOU.

215
00:10:20,208 --> 00:10:21,500
YOU'RE THE ONE WHO'S
GETTING ME INTO TROUBLE.

216
00:10:21,583 --> 00:10:22,583
( grunts )

217
00:10:22,666 --> 00:10:24,500
- PRINCESS SASAMI AND OTHERS

218
00:10:24,583 --> 00:10:26,500
THAT WERE INVOLVED
IN THIS ATTEMPTED COUP

219
00:10:26,583 --> 00:10:28,791
ARE STILL AT LARGE
WITH THE PRINCESS AYEKA.

220
00:10:28,875 --> 00:10:31,250
AND THE POLICE ARE DOING
EVERYTHING THEY CAN

221
00:10:31,333 --> 00:10:32,708
TO APPREHEND THEM.

222
00:10:32,791 --> 00:10:34,708
- I'D BETTER TELL KIYONE
ABOUT THE NEWS.

223
00:10:34,791 --> 00:10:36,708
( slurps )

224
00:10:36,791 --> 00:10:37,875
AHH.

225
00:10:41,041 --> 00:10:42,541
- YO!

226
00:10:55,875 --> 00:10:57,791
- AYEKA,

227
00:10:57,875 --> 00:11:00,125
YOU ARE BEING FRAMED.

228
00:11:00,208 --> 00:11:03,333
- I ASK YOU AGAIN,
WHERE IS PRINCESS AYEKA?

229
00:11:03,416 --> 00:11:05,041
YOU MUST TELL ME,
KIYONE.

230
00:11:05,125 --> 00:11:06,750
- I DON'T KNOW, SIR.

231
00:11:08,958 --> 00:11:09,916
- I SEE.

232
00:11:14,625 --> 00:11:16,125
- ( elevator dings )

